metadata.name: Hidden SpaceFud
metadata.description: SpaceFuds is a love for Sci-Fi community driven collectibles NFT project. 10k SpaceFud NFTs are made up with over a hundred futuristic and electrifying traits. Each SpaceFud is a unique NFT on the Ethereum blockchain and holders are allowed to participate in the coordination of the SpaceShip Vault, which will be filled with 130 ETH after all SpaceFuds have been minted.
